'''Abadam''' un hukuma pamarun der [[Diiwal Borno]] [[Niiseriya]] ɗun fuuna weɗuu ɓela Chadi. Hautirɗe ɗen eɗa ɗer gelle Malum Fatori. Eɗi woodi geɓeɗe 3,973km2 e ɗuɗirka yimɓe 100,180 limgal 2006. Lamba wuro noddirga geɓel gel hanka woni 602.<ref>http://www.nipost.gov.ng/PostCode.aspx | accessdate = 2009-10-20 | archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20091007011423/http://www.nipost.gov.ng/PostCode.aspx| archivedate= 7 October 2009 | url-status= dead}}</ref>
Eɗe go’o eɗer hukumaji pamari sappo e jewe go’o e ɗun latiɗun lamorde Borno, diiwal gal ungal areji naneneno Borno ha Najeriya.<ref>https://books.google.com/books| edition = Millennium
